  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2018-1245<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2018-10-03</p><hr><p>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nHer Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Prime Minister, fixes the remuneration, in the amount and on the date indicated in the annexed schedule, of:\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nDenis, Richard, interim Clerk of the Senate and Clerk of the Parliaments, within the range GC 6 ($148,900 - $175,100), effective April 1, 2018;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nDi Lorenzo, Assunta, Secretary to the Governor General, within the range ($192,600 - $226,500), effective April 1, 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nDufresne, Philippe, Law Clerk and Parliamentary Counsel of the House of Commons, within the range ($171,200 - $200,300), effective April 1, 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’Heureux, Sonia, former Parliamentary Librarian, within the range GC 7 ($171,200 - $201,300), commencing on April 1, 2018 and ending on June 20, 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nMarcoux, Rennie, Executive Director of the Secretariat of the National Security and Intelligence Committee of Parliamentarians, within the range ($172,200 - $202,500), effective April 1, 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nMounier, Marie-Geneviève, Associate Secretary to the Governor General, within the range ($171,200 - $201,300), effective April 1, 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nPeters, John Gregory, Usher of the Black Rod, within the range GC 3 ($98,100 - $115,300), effective April 1, 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:right;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:right;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n…/2</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-indent:2.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n- 2 -\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nProulx, Nicole, former interim Clerk of the Senate and Clerk of the Parliaments, within the range ($171,200 - $200,300), commencing on July 10, 2017 and ending on January 30, 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nRobert, Charles, Clerk of the House of Commons, within the range GC 8 ($196,600 - $231,200), effective April 1, 2018; and\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nWallace, Stephen, former Secretary to the Governor General, within the range ($192,600 - $226,500), commencing on April 1, 2017 and ending on December 29, 2017.\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSur recommandation du premier ministre, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil fixe la rémunération, conformément au montant et à la date indiquée dans l’annexe ci-jointe, de :\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nDenis, Richard, greffier du Sénat et greffier des Parlements par intérim, dans l’échelle GC 6 (148 900 $ – 175 100 $), à compter du 1<sup>er </sup>avril 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nDi Lorenzo, Assunta, secrétaire de la gouverneure générale, dans l’échelle (192 600 $ – 226 500 $), à compter du 1<sup>er</sup> avril 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nDufresne, Philippe, secrétaire légiste et conseiller parlementaire de la Chambre des communes, dans l’échelle (171 200 $ – 200 300 $), à compter du 1<sup>er </sup>avril 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’Heureux, Sonia, ancienne bibliothécaire parlementaire, dans l’échelle GC 7 (171 200 $ – 201 300 $), commençant le 1<sup>er</sup> avril 2018 et se terminant le 20 juin 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nMarcoux, Rennie, directrice générale du Secrétariat du Comité des parlementaires sur la sécurité nationale et le renseignement, dans l’échelle (172 200 $ – 202 500 $), à compter du 1<sup>er</sup> avril 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nMounier, Marie-Geneviève, secrétaire déléguée de la gouverneure générale, dans l’échelle (171 200 $ – 201 300 $), à compter du 1<sup>er</sup> avril 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nPeters, John Gregory, huissier du Bâton noir, dans l’échelle GC 3 (98 100 $ – 115 300 $), à compter du 1<sup>er</sup> avril 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:right;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n…/2</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-indent:2.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n- 2 -\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nProulx, Nicole, ancienne greffière du Sénat et greffière des Parlements par intérim, dans l’échelle (171 200 $ – 200 300 $), commençant le 10 juillet 2017 et se terminant le 30 janvier 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nRobert, Charles, greffier de la Chambre des communes, dans l’échelle GC 8 (196 600 $ – 231 200 $), à compter du 1<sup>er</sup> avril 2018;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nWallace, Stephen, ancien secrétaire du gouverneur général, dans l’échelle (192 600 $ – 226 500 $), commençant le 1<sup>er</sup> avril 2017 et se terminant le 29 décembre 2017.</p>\n\n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n            var defPreFooter = document.getElementById(\"def-preFooter\");\n            defPreFooter.outerHTML = wet.builder.preFooter({\n                cdnEnv: \"prod\",\n                dateModified: \"2022-07-11\",\n                showPostContent: true\n            });\n        </script>\n    "
